### Get list of valid event types via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
GET {{ingress_base_url}}/event-types
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Create a new client subscription via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
POST {{ingress_base_url}}/client-subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: d679fd61-061f-4440-9623-36280f0807b7

{
  "notificationEndpoint": {
    "callbackUrl": "https://client.example.com/events"
  },
  "eventTypes": ["PRISON_COURT_REGISTER_GENERATED"]
}

###

### Get a client subscription by ID via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
GET {{ingress_base_url}}/client-subscriptions/{{client_subscription_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Correlation-Id: d679fd61-061f-4440-9623-36280f0807b7

###

### Update a client subscription by ID via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
PUT {{ingress_base_url}}/client-subscriptions/{{client_subscription_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: d679fd61-061f-4440-9623-36280f0807b7

{
  "notificationEndpoint": {
    "callbackUrl": "https://client.example.com/new-hook"
  },
  "eventTypes": ["PRISON_COURT_REGISTER_GENERATED"]
}

###

### Delete a client subscription by ID via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
DELETE {{ingress_base_url}}/client-subscriptions/{{client_subscription_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Correlation-Id: d679fd61-061f-4440-9623-36280f0807b7

###

### Create a notification (Internal) via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
POST {{ingress_base_url}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: d679fd61-061f-4440-9623-36280f0807b7

{
  "eventId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "materialId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "eventType": "PRISON_COURT_REGISTER_GENERATED",
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
  "defendant": {
    "masterDefendantId": "8b8f1c3a-9a41-4f0f-b8a0-1c23d9e8a111",
    "name": "John Doe",
    "dateOfBirth": "1990-05-15",
    "custodyEstablishmentDetails": {
      "emailAddress": "prison@moj.gov.uk"
    },
    "cases": [
      { "urn": "CT98KRYCAP" },
      { "urn": "AB75123123" }
    ]
  }
}

###

### Get PDF document for a subscription via Ingress (bypasses WAF + APIM)
GET {{ingress_base_url}}/client-subscriptions/{{client_subscription_id}}/documents/{{document_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Correlation-Id: d679fd61-061f-4440-9623-36280f0807b7

###